<description>
<p>The action-arcade game with spells and somersaults!

This is the game where you can play as the Wizard and doing many spells! You need to come through eight locations. Dodges from enemies and it's bullets. Fast changing between spells and also have understanding which spell you needing use now. And Finally! Get fight with the Final Boss!</p>
<p><b>Features:</b></p>
  <ul>
    <li>Spelling any of the eight spells!</li>
    <li>Doing somersaults and dodging out of enemies and it's bullets!</li>
    <li>Many locations with different events!</li>
    <li>Get fighting with the Final Boss!</li>
  </ol>
</description>

